ingredientsDesc:
1.Tubes coated with anti AFP (monoclonal antibodies), (2 x 48 or 8 x 48 tubes)
2.Tracer：125Iodine labelled anti-AFP (monoclonal antibody) in phosphate buffer with bovine serum albumin, azide (<0.1%) and inert red dye (1 vail, 10.5 ml, 350 kBq or 4 vials, 10.5 ml, 4 x 350 kBq)

6.Controls 1 or 2 in human serum with merthiolate (2 or 2 x 2 vials lyophil.)
